<div id="pf61" class="pf wc h0" data-page-no="61"><div class="pc pc61 wc h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 wd h1" alt="" src="bg61.png"/><div class="t m174 x69 h31 ybf0 ff3 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons for Second Quarter, 1989 </div><div class="t m34c x6d hd ybf1 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath School members who have not received a copy of the Adult </div><div class="t m6a8 x1b hd yadc ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons for the second quarter of 1989 will be helped by the following </div><div class="t m2c8 x1b hd ybf2 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">outline in studying the first two lessons. The title of the series is &quot;Christ </div><div class="t m2c4 x1b hd yade ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for Time and Eternity.&quot; This quarter&apos;s lessons cover the first half of the </div><div class="t m18e x1b hd ybf3 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book of Revelation. </div><div class="t m2c6 x1b h31 y85 ff3 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">First Lesson: </div><div class="t mfd x1b hd ybf4 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;BLESSED IS BE WHO READS&quot; </div><div class="t m6a9 x20 hd y6fe ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY TEXT: Revelation 1:3. </div><div class="t m6aa x20 hd ybf5 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THIS WEEK&apos;S STUDY: Revelation 1:1-8. </div><div class="t mc6 x6d hd ybf6 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WHY THIS LESSON IS IMPORTANT TO YOU: The message of the </div><div class="t m51a x1b hd ybf7 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book of Revelation was given by God to enable you to prepare for the </div><div class="t m227 x5f hd ybf8 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">second coming of Jesus. </div><div class="t m1a5 x20 hd y829 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OUTLINE: </div><div class="t m57 x0 hd y84 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"></span></div><div class="t m6ab x77 hd ybf9 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">L </div><div class="t m57 x93 hd ybf9 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m664 x73 hd y82a ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Divine Revelation (Revelation 1:1, 2). </div><div class="t m57 x0 hd y84 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0